    "A careful guide for digging into topics and weighing sources." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein sorgfältiger Begleiter, um Themen zu durchdringen und Quellen abzuwägen."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "주제를 파고들고 출처를 평가하기 위한 신중한 가이드입니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "一个细致的向导，帮你深入探究主题并权衡资料来源。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A connected peer is running “%@”." : {
      "comment" : "In-app toast message shown on the host when a connected remote peer runs one of its agents. %@ is the agent name.",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Ein verbundener Peer führt „%@“ aus."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "연결된 피어가 “%@”을(를) 실행하고 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "已连接的对等节点正在运行“%@”。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A device wants to pair with **%@**.\nAllow this device to connect?" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein Gerät möchte sich mit **%@** koppeln.\nDieses Gerät verbinden lassen?"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "기기가 **%@**와(과) 페어링하려고 합니다.\n이 기기의 연결을 허용하시겠습니까?"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "有设备想要与 **%@** 配对。\n允许此设备连接吗？"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A file came back at the wrong size, which usually means the connection was interrupted. Retrying should fix this." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "A file came back at the wrong size, which usually means the connection was interrupted. Retrying should fix this."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "파일이 잘못된 크기로 반환되었습니다. 이는 일반적으로 연결이 중단되었음을 의미합니다. 다시 시도하면 이 문제가 해결될 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "文件返回时大小不正确，通常是连接中断所致。重试即可修复。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A focused helper for planning, todos, and staying on track." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein fokussierter Helfer fürs Planen, To-dos und den Überblick."
