    "A schema migration failed, so the database couldn't be upgraded to this build's format." : {
      "comment" : "Description of a memory database failure when a schema migration failed.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Eine Schemamigration ist fehlgeschlagen, so dass die Datenbank nicht auf das Format dieses Builds aktualisiert werden konnte."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "스키마 마이그레이션에 실패하여 데이터베이스를 이 빌드의 형식으로 업그레이드할 수 없습니다."
