    "Define your own regex patterns — internal codenames, customer IDs, anything Osaurus's built-ins don't cover. Bad patterns are validated before save." : {
      "comment" : "A description under the \"Custom Rules\" section, explaining that users can create their own regex patterns to identify sensitive information.",
