    "Discover and run models already on this Mac from other tools. Osaurus references these files in place and never copies, modifies, or deletes them." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the feature that allows users to discover and run models that already live on their Mac from other tools, like the Hugging Face Hub cache or LM Studio.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Discover and run models already on this Mac from other tools. Osaurus references these files in place and never copies, modifies, or deletes them."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "다른 도구에서 이 Mac에 이미 있는 모델을 발견하고 실행하세요. Osaurus는 이러한 파일을 제자리에서 참조하며 복사, 수정 또는 삭제하지 않습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "发现并运行这台 Mac 上已有的其他工具中的模型。Osaurus 就地引用这些文件，从不复制、修改或删除它们。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
