    "Each generated AppleScript is shown for your approval before it runs." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual"
    },
    "Each helper is off by default. Turn one on to set it up." : {
      "comment" : "Help text for the \"Subagents\" tab in the Agent Detail View, explaining that each helper is off by default and that turning one on allows the user to set it up.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Jeder Helfer ist standardmäßig deaktiviert. Schalten Sie einen ein, um ihn einzurichten."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "각 도우미는 기본적으로 꺼져 있습니다. 설정하려면 하나를 켜세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "每个助手默认都是关闭的。开启其中一个以进行设置。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Each line is matched literally — no regex needed. Special characters are escaped for you." : {
      "comment" : "A description below the text field where the user enters multiple terms for a \"Terms\" rule.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Each line is matched literally — no regex needed. Special characters are escaped for you."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "각 줄은 문자 그대로 일치합니다. 정규식이 필요하지 않습니다. 특수 문자는 자동으로 이스케이프됩니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "每行均按字面内容进行匹配——无需正则表达式。特殊字符将自动为您转义。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Each one gets its own access, and you can take it back any time." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Jeder erhält seinen eigenen Zugang, und du kannst ihn jederzeit zurücknehmen."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "각각 고유한 액세스 권한을 가지며 언제든지 회수할 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "每一个都有自己的访问权限，你可以随时收回。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
