    "Establishing the Osaurus Secure Channel — forward-secret, mutually authenticated end-to-end encryption. Not encrypted until connected." : {
      "comment" : "Help text for the empty-state security badge while a remote agent connection is still being established.",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Der Osaurus Secure Channel wird aufgebaut – vorwärtsgeheime, gegenseitig authentifizierte Ende-zu-Ende-Verschlüsselung. Bis zur Verbindung nicht verschlüsselt."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Osaurus 보안 채널 설정 중 — 순방향 비밀성(forward-secret)이 보장되는 상호 인증 종단간 암호화입니다. 연결될 때까지는 암호화되지 않습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "正在建立 Osaurus 安全通道——前向保密、相互认证的端到端加密。连接前不加密。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
