      "shouldTranslate" : false
    },
    "Give agents a dedicated on-device model that writes and runs AppleScript to automate this Mac — controlling apps like Finder, Safari, Mail, Notes, and System Events. Turn it on per agent in the Agents tab; download a model below to make it available." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual"
    },
    "Give the agent a tool it can call to read a reply aloud when you ask. For always-speak, use Auto Speak Responses in the Voice section." : {
      "comment" : "A description of a feature toggle that lets an agent read its responses aloud.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Give the agent a tool it can call to read a reply aloud when you ask. For always-speak, use Auto Speak Responses in the Voice section."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "요청 시 에이전트가 답변을 소리 내어 읽을 수 있도록 호출할 수 있는 도구를 제공합니다. 항상 말하게 하려면 음성 섹션에서 답변 자동 말하기를 사용하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "当您提问时，给智能体一个它可以调用的工具来朗读回复。如需始终朗读，请在语音部分使用“自动朗读回复”。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Give the agent a tool to drive macOS apps via the accessibility tree — clicking, typing, and reading on-screen content. Reads and navigation run automatically; edits and anything consequential pause for your approval." : {
      "comment" : "A description of a feature that lets an agent interact with macOS apps using",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Geben Sie dem Agenten ein Werkzeug, um macOS-Apps über den Barrierefreiheitsbaum zu steuern — Klicken, Tippen und Lesen von Bildschirminhalten. Lesen und Navigation werden automatisch ausgeführt; Bearbeitungen und alles mit realen Auswirkungen werden zur Genehmigung angehalten."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "접근성 트리를 통해 macOS 앱을 구동할 수 있는 도구를 에이전트에 제공합니다 — 화면 내용 클릭, 입력 및 읽기. 읽기 및 탐색은 자동으로 실행되며, 편집 및 결과에 영향을 미치는 모든 작업은 승인을 위해 일시 중지됩니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "给予智能体一个工具，通过辅助功能树来控制 macOS 应用程序——点击、输入和读取屏幕内容。读取和导航操作会自动运行，但编辑和任何重要操作则会暂停，等待您的批准。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Give the agent the spawn / local_delegate / image_generate / image_edit tools — it can offload bounded tasks to a subagent persona or a local model, and generate or edit images. Default models, RAM-safety, and permissions are configured in Settings → Spawn." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Give the agent the spawn / local_delegate / image_generate / image_edit tools — it can offload bounded tasks to a subagent persona or a local model, and generate or edit images. Default models, RAM-safety, and permissions are configured in Settings → Spawn."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Give the agent the spawn / local_delegate / image_generate / image_edit tools — it can offload bounded tasks to a subagent persona or a local model, and generate or edit images. Default models, RAM-safety, and permissions are configured in Settings → Spawn."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "赋予代理 spawn / local_delegate / image_generate / image_edit 工具——它可以将有界任务卸载给子代理角色或本地模型，并生成或编辑图片。默认模型、内存安全和权限在“设置 → 生成”中配置。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Give the assistant ambient awareness of what you're working on. When on, Osaurus freezes a quick snapshot of your open windows and the field you're focused on at the start of each chat, and shares it as background context. It's built from on-screen text only — no screenshots — and is scrubbed by the Privacy Filter before it reaches a cloud model." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Give the assistant ambient awareness of what you're working on. When on, Osaurus freezes a quick snapshot of your open windows and the field you're focused on at the start of each chat, and shares it as background context. It's built from on-screen text only — no screenshots — and is scrubbed by the Privacy Filter before it reaches a cloud model."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "작업 중인 내용에 대한 주변 인식(ambient awareness)을 어시스턴트에게 제공합니다. 켜져 있으면 Osaurus는 각 채팅이 시작될 때 열려 있는 창과 초점을 맞춘 필드의 빠른 스냅샷을 고정하고 이를 배경 컨텍스트로 공유합니다. 화면의 텍스트로만 구성되며 스크린샷은 포함되지 않으며, 클라우드 모델에 도달하기 전에 개인정보 필터에 의해 비식별화됩니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "让助手获得你正在处理内容的环境感知。开启后，Osaurus 会在每次对话开始时，快速捕捉你打开的窗口与当前聚焦的输入框，定格为一帧快照，并将其作为背景上下文传给助手。该快照仅提取屏幕文字，不含截图，并会在发送给云端模型前经隐私过滤器清洗。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Give this agent a private encrypted database to remember structured data across runs." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the \"Database\" feature toggle in the Agent Detail View.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Gib diesem Agenten eine private verschlüsselte Datenbank, um strukturierte Daten über Läufe hinweg zu speichern."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "실행 간에 구조화된 데이터를 기억할 수 있도록 이 에이전트에 비공개 암호화된 데이터베이스를 제공합니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "为此智能体提供一个私有的加密数据库，以便跨多次运行记住结构化数据。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
