    "Leave empty to allow Computer Use in any app. Add apps to restrict it to ONLY those — every other app is blocked before any action." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the app allowlist feature, explaining that it allows Computer Use in any app by default, and lets you add specific apps to restrict it to only those.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Leer lassen, um Computer Use in jeder App zuzulassen. Fügen Sie Apps hinzu, um Computer Use NUR auf diese zu beschränken — jede andere App wird vor jeder Aktion blockiert."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "모든 앱에서 컴퓨터 사용을 허용하려면 비워 두세요. 특정 앱만 허용하려면 앱을 추가하세요 — 추가된 앱을 제외한 다른 모든 앱은 작업 전에 차단됩니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "留空则允许在任何应用中使用电脑操作。添加应用则限制为仅允许这些——其他所有应用在执行任何操作前都会被阻止。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Leave empty to only use agent names as wake words" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Leer lassen, um nur Agentennamen als Aktivierungswörter zu nutzen"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "에이전트 이름만 호출어로 사용하려면 비워 두세요"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "留空则仅使用智能体名称作为唤醒词"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Leave empty to use default values from global settings." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Leer lassen, um Standardwerte aus den globalen Einstellungen zu verwenden."
          }
        },
