          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "让智能体在你的消息之间采取行动。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Let the agent automate this Mac by writing and running AppleScript with an on-device model. Each script is shown for your approval or auto-run with a warning, per the mode below." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual"
    },
    "Let the agent control macOS apps for you — clicking, typing, and reading the screen. Reads and navigation run automatically; edits and anything consequential pause for your approval." : {
      "comment" : "Subtitle for the \"Computer Use\" per-agent capability card in the Agent Detail View.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Lassen Sie den Agenten macOS-Apps für Sie steuern — klicken, tippen und den Bildschirm lesen. Lese- und Navigationsvorgänge laufen automatisch; Änderungen und alles Wichtige warten auf Ihre Genehmigung."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "에이전트가 macOS 앱을 제어할 수 있도록 허용합니다 — 클릭, 타이핑, 화면 읽기. 읽기 및 탐색은 자동으로 실행되며, 편집 및 중요한 작업은 승인을 위해 일시 정지됩니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "允许智能体为您控制 macOS 应用 — 点击、输入与读取屏幕内容。读取与导航操作自动执行；编辑及其它有后果的操作将暂停并等待您批准。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Let the agent create its own tools as plugins." : {
      "comment" : "A feature toggle that lets an agent create its own tools as plugins.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lass den Agenten eigene Tools als Plugins erstellen."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "에이전트가 자신의 도구를 플러그인으로 생성하도록 허용합니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "让智能体以插件形式创建自己的工具。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Let the agent generate and edit images with a local model using the `image` tool." : {
