            "value" : "允许模型在客户端未显式指定 `tool_choice` 时调用工具。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Let the server release memory when no requests are in flight." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Let the server release memory when no requests are in flight."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "진행 중인 요청이 없을 때 서버가 메모리를 해제하도록 허용합니다."
          }
        },
