    "Local endpoints don't usually need a key — leave blank to skip auth." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lokale Endpunkte benötigen normalerweise keinen Schlüssel – leer lassen, um die Authentifizierung zu überspringen."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "로컬 엔드포인트는 일반적으로 키가 필요하지 않습니다 — 인증을 건너뛰려면 비워 두세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "本地端点通常不需要密钥——留空即可跳过身份验证。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Local Guide" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
