    "On approve, your device will fetch a private access key from the agent's server. The agent's owner can revoke this at any time." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the functionality of the \"Approve\" button in the IncomingPairSheet.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nach der Genehmigung ruft dein Gerät einen privaten Zugriffsschlüssel vom Server des Agenten ab. Der Besitzer des Agenten kann diesen jederzeit widerrufen."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "승인하면 기기가 에이전트의 서버에서 비공개 접근 키를 가져옵니다. 에이전트 소유자는 언제든지 이를 취소할 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "批准后，你的设备将从智能体的服务器获取一个私有访问密钥。智能体的所有者可随时撤销此密钥。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "On Device" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Auf dem Gerät"
          }
        },
