    "The storage encryption key is unavailable on this Mac (Keychain reset, app re-sign, or migration without iCloud Keychain). Your encrypted memory can't be unlocked with the current key." : {
      "comment" : "Detailed explanation of why the memory database can't be unlocked.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Der Speicherverschlüsselungsschlüssel ist auf diesem Mac nicht verfügbar (Schlüsselbund zurücksetzen, App neu signieren oder Migration ohne iCloud-Schlüsselbund). Ihre verschlüsselte Speicher kann mit dem aktuellen Schlüssel nicht entsperrt werden."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "이 Mac에서는 저장소 암호화 키를 사용할 수 없습니다(키체인 재설정, 앱 재서명 또는 iCloud 키체인 없이 마이그레이션). 현재 키로는 암호화된 메모리의 잠금을 해제할 수 없습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此Mac上的存储加密密钥不可用（钥匙串重置、应用程序重新签名或未使用iCloud钥匙串进行迁移）。无法使用当前密钥解密您的加密内存。"
          }
        }
      }
