      }
    },
    "These agents had no machine-readable schedule and were created disabled. Tap one to set a cron expression:" : {
      "comment" : "A message explaining that some agents need their schedules configured.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Diese Agenten hatten keinen maschinenlesbaren Zeitplan und wurden deaktiviert erstellt. Tippe auf einen, um einen Cron-Ausdruck festzulegen:"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "이 에이전트는 기계가 읽을 수 있는 일정이 없어 사용 안 함으로 생성되었습니다. 하나를 탭하여 cron 표현식을 설정하세요:"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这些智能体没有机器可读的计划，创建时为禁用状态。点击其中一个以设置 cron 表达式："
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These apply to the main chat and any agent set to choose automatically. Each agent can override them in its own Subagents settings." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual"
    },
    "These artifacts couldn't be installed:" : {
      "localizations" : {
