            "value" : "正在思考"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This agent advertised that it supports encryption but didn't include a verifiable identity, so it can't be paired securely. It may be impersonating another device, or the other device may need to update Osaurus." : {
      "comment" : "A description of why an agent that claims Secure Channel support (`osc=1`) but doesn't include a verifiable identity (a crypto address) is not trustworthy.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "This agent advertised that it supports encryption but didn't include a verifiable identity, so it can't be paired securely. It may be impersonating another device, or the other device may need to update Osaurus."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "This agent advertised that it supports encryption but didn't include a verifiable identity, so it can't be paired securely. It may be impersonating another device, or the other device may need to update Osaurus."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此代理声称支持加密但未包含可验证的身份，因此无法安全配对。它可能在冒充其他设备，或者对方设备可能需要更新 Osaurus。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This agent has no memory tables yet." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dieser Agent hat noch keine Speichertabellen."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "이 에이전트에는 아직 메모리 테이블이 없습니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此智能体还没有记忆表。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This agent has no shareable identity. Pair it over your network or generate a relay invite from the header Share button, then connected peers will appear here." : {
      "comment" : "A hint text that appears when an agent has no shareable identity and there are no connected peers.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "This agent has no shareable identity. Pair it over your network or generate a relay invite from the header Share button, then connected peers will appear here."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "이 에이전트에는 공유 가능한 ID가 없습니다. 네트워크를 통해 페어링하거나 헤더의 공유 버튼에서 릴레이 초대를 생성하면 연결된 피어가 여기에 표시됩니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "该代理暂无可以分享的身份。请通过网络进行配对，或点击顶部\"分享\"按钮生成中继邀请，已连接的对等端将显示在此处。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This agent's database is approaching its storage quota." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
