      }
    },
    "This bundle advertises DFlash/speculative-decoding metadata, but local generation has no target/draft acceptance contract or benchmark proof yet. Use it only after native runtime support lands." : {
      "comment" : "Warning about using a DFlash/speculative-decoding-capable model that has not yet been proven to work on the host.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "This bundle advertises DFlash/speculative-decoding metadata, but local generation has no target/draft acceptance contract or benchmark proof yet. Use it only after native runtime support lands."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "이 번들은 DFlash/speculative-decoding 메타데이터를 알리지만, 로컬 생성에는 아직 target/draft 수락 계약이나 벤치마크 증명이 없습니다. 네이티브 런타임 지원이 제공된 후에만 사용하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此包声明了 DFlash/推测解码元数据，但本地生成尚无目标/草稿接受契约或基准证明。请在原生运行时支持落地后再使用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This bundle isn't in MLX format, so the local engine (vmlx) can't load it. Osaurus runs MLX-format weights only — convert it with mlx_lm or pick an MLX build of the model." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Dieses Paket ist nicht im MLX-Format, daher kann die lokale Engine (vmlx) es nicht laden. Osaurus führt nur MLX-Format-Gewichte aus — konvertieren Sie es mit mlx_lm oder wählen Sie eine MLX-Version des Modells."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "이 번들은 MLX 형식이 아니므로 로컬 엔진(vmlx)이 로드할 수 없습니다. Osaurus는 MLX 형식 가중치만 실행합니다 — mlx_lm으로 변환하거나 MLX 빌드를 선택하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这个捆绑包不是MLX格式，因此本地引擎(vmlx)无法加载它。Osaurus只能运行MLX格式的权重——请使用mlx_lm进行转换，或选择该模型的MLX版本。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This bundle isn't ready" : {
      "comment" : "A title for a card indicating that a model bundle is not yet available.",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
